name: Nyzio Tree Stump Removal
tag_list: tree-stump-removal, tree-stump-grinding, stump-removal, stump-grinding, tree-services, shrub-and-tree-services
overview:
Owner operated stump grinding service operating in Philadelphia, New Jersey and Delaware. All Nyzio Tree Stump Removal does is remove stumps. They work for homeowners, tree contractors, golf courses, building contractors or anyone who may need one or more stumps removed. Large or small stumps they have the equipment that can get the job completed. Same day service is available. They also have the ability to remove the entire stump so you can plant in the same area. Most stumps are ground down to a dept of 6 inches so top soil and grass seed can installed and the memory of the tree forgotten. Estimates can be given over the phone or email.

Contact info: Nyzio Tree Stump Removal 2131 Basswood Dr Lafayette Hill, PA 19444 (610) 656-9543 http://www.treestump-removal.com/
